    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter">
                <head type="title">Cornelis De Schrijver to Miklós Oláh (Antwerp, 24 September
                    1536)</head>
                <floatingText>
                    <body>
                        <p>He is sending the piece he has written for the Queen, which his brother
                            has printed, along with other works he has published. He placed an
                            epigram on the cover so the whole world knows how good Oláh has been to
                            him. He is also sending the epigrams he wrote on Erasmus of Rotterdam’s
                            death. He is recommending him to Cornelis de Schepper and Maximiliaan
                            van Zevenbergen.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p>Cornelius Grapheus Nicolao Olao salutem. </p>
                <p>Magnifice Domine! Quem dicavi augustissimae
                        <persName>reginae</persName> libellum,<note type="critic"><hi rend="italic"
                            >Ad optimam heroidem Mariam, Hungariae reginam, sacrorum bucolicorum
                            aeglogae tres</hi>, see Ep.
                        551.</note><ref>/o:olahus.tei.15351201_1</ref> eum una cum aliis nonnullis
                    per <persName>fratrem</persName><note type="critic">Johannes Grapheus was a
                        printer in Antwerp.</note> meum excusum, <milestone unit="pb"/>tandem ad te mitto. Ut autem mundus non ignoret tuum erga me
                    beneficium, nempe te mihi exhibendo libello apud reginam fuisse ducem, posui pro
                    fronte libelli epigramma, quo mea Musa meam erga te testatur gratitudinem.
                    Epitaphia quoque, quae <persName>Erasmo</persName> demortuo scripsi, ad te cum
                    praesentibus misi. Te vero oro, ut haec qualia, qualia sunt, boni consulas. Vale
                    et me amicis commenda, praesertim domino <persName>Cornelio
                        Sceppero</persName><note type="critic">Cornelis de Schepper.</note> et
                        <persName>Maximiliano Transilvano</persName>,<note type="critic">Maximiliaan
                        van Zevenbergen.</note> ad quem quoque privatim scribo. Rursum vale. </p>
                <p><placeName>Antverpiae</placeName> VIII. Kalendas Octobris anno MDXXXVI. </p>
                <p
                    ><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>[Epitaphium
                    domini Erasmi Roterodami per Grapheum]<?oxy_custom_end?><note type="critic"><hi
                            rend="smallcap">Ipolyi</hi> 1875, 586–587. In Romanian: <hi
                            rend="smallcap">Albu–Capoianu</hi> 1974, 157–158.
                    </note><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?></p>
                <p>[Aliud]<?oxy_custom_end?><note type="critic"><hi rend="smallcap"
                            >Ipolyi</hi> 1875, 587. In Romanian: <hi rend="smallcap"
